  m_Name: Death - After Oldrion
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  data:
    convoName: Death - After Oldrion
    lines:
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'You really did it. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Why are you still here? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'Like I told you; I am a guide for the dead. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: " \u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I never thought the afterlife would be so\u2026 peaceful. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'Who said you were in the afterlife? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'What are you saying? Am I still alive? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "I didn\u2019t say that, either. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'Then where are we? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Everywhere, Orion. And nowhere. From here, celestial beings watch over
        their domain, the way I watched you. I\u2019ve seen your entire journey,
        from beginning to end. And we both know you made many poor decisions in your
        time, but when it mattered most, you took responsibility.  "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Your years have made you wise. No doubt you now understand that life
        everlasting is no gift at all\u2013 that stories carry no meaning in the
        absence of a conclusion. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: 'So, Orion, I have something to offer you. '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: 'An offering from Death? A reward, I suppose? '
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "Not exactly. You see, every being\u2019s time must eventually come to
        an end\u2026 and that includes mine. Since the dawn of time, I have been
        carrying out my responsibilities, but now I know I am ready to pass them
        on to someone new. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "And you think that\u2019s me? "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "You\u2019ll live for a long while more, helping to guide the dead to
        their destinations. Then, like me, you will eventually pick a successor. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "The old me would have leapt at this opportunity. To gain effective immortality.
        But now\u2026 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Death
      expression: 
      line: "I have watched your journey, Orion, and I know you are ready for this.
        Your life was a reign of terror and destruction, but now you may atone by
        being humanity\u2019s final stepping stone. "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: "I\u2013 "
      audio: {fileID: 0}
    - character: Orion
      expression: 
      line: I understand. And I am prepared.
      audio: {fileID: 0}
